text: U&Gold; is a British pay television channel from the UKTV network, that was launched on 1 November 1992 as UK Gold before it was rebranded UKTV Gold in 2004, G.O.L.D in 2008 and finally Gold in 2010. == Other websites == * Category:British television channels Category:1992 establishments in the United Kingdom
title: Gold (British TV channel)
